    "description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>THE FORGOTTEN AI</i></strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden inside an old program somewhere lies Emily, a long forgotten AI, lonely. She seems to know way more than she lets on, it's up to you to discover what secrets she's hiding and to unearth the mysteries that reside deep within the program. How much does she really know? There are too many unaswered questions and the more you look the more seem to come up</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100780/extras/82e438c49b9e342d6746d60ed7828337.avif?t=1747307197\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100780/extras_big/82e438c49b9e342d6746d60ed7828337.avif?t=1747307197 width=800 height=446 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>CHAT WITH EMILY</i></strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the game you'll have the opportunity to chat with Emily and although you don't know anything about her, she seems to know more than she lets on about you. Emily is willing to chat but sometimes your connection to the chatroom gets severed, if you wanto to uncover the truth you'll have to push trough and get her to tell you everything... but maybe there's another way to get some informations</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100780/extras/4d07ad6a201959bf29aada8e2e07c7d1.poster.avif?t=1747307197\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100780/extras/4d07ad6a201959bf29aada8e2e07c7d1.webm?t=1747307197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100780/extras/4d07ad6a201959bf29aada8e2e07c7d1.mp4?t=1747307197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>SECRET CODES</i></strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The program also features a database with many secret files, each locked behind a code. Inside there's everything from messages to audio recordings and even video files. This codes could be anything, and each code is linked to the content of the file. The truth must be there somewhere so you'll have to try to figure out those codes. This files are old, left by someone who used to work on this program, someone linked to this whole thing, someone who knew the truth</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100780/extras/f36fab2ee8dcf4d8efc86553cde0833d.avif?t=1747307197\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100780/extras_big/f36fab2ee8dcf4d8efc86553cde0833d.avif?t=1747307197 width=800 height=448 /></span></p>",
